All of us who having a ways of studying by oneself, it follow us from our schooling to now. But these ways whether is profit of us.

Studying ways is importance of us. Studying is a less of difficult if we holding some efficient ways. Sure, studying motivation is also necessary, although you holding some ways of studying, it is possible of you have no progress. So studying motivation take you to next stage. If you just only holding motivation of studying, when you would like to next stage, you will spend a lot time, and finally it is possible of failure.

From view of me, you can ask your classmates or senior for ways of studying. In order to keep studying motivation, you should be relax yourself when you feel rired.